description:
Modded Minecraft. In this Minecraft episode we team up with Arkas to defend the castle for as long as possible against the mighty siege of the server.

This is the season finale for this map, but it is not the end of the CrackPack server. We will be restarting on a new map shortly, with new players, an improved plan, and hopefully less technical problems. More details will be revealed in the next episode.

MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

Mod Pack: http://www.atlauncher.com/pack/TheCrackPack/
MindCrack: http://www.youtube.com/user/MindCrackNetwork
